Sentencas: Performance of thin film solid oxide fuel cells (TF-SOFCs) were improved by inserting plasma enhanced atomic layer deposition (PEALD) of yttira-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) interlayers.
Titulo: Effects of Nanoscale PEALD YSZ Interlayer for AAO Based Thin Film Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: By controlling the ratio between Y2O3 and ZrO2 in YSZ deposition supercycles, Y2O3 mol.% in YSZ films were changed.
Titulo: Effects of Nanoscale PEALD YSZ Interlayer for AAO Based Thin Film Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: High Y2O3 contained PEALD YSZ interlayered cell showed higher maximum power density (123.6 mW/cm(2) at 500 degrees C, 286.1 mW/cm(2) at 550 degrees C) and smaller polarization resistance compared with reference Y2O3 concentrated PEALD YSZ interlayer cell.
Titulo: Effects of Nanoscale PEALD YSZ Interlayer for AAO Based Thin Film Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: (108.5 mW/cm(2) at 500 degrees C, 181.1 mW/cm(2) at 550 degrees C) Exchange current densities of TF-SOFCs at 500 degrees C also improved ~ 59.3% at high Y2O3 concentrated PEALD YSZ interlayer cells.
Titulo: Effects of Nanoscale PEALD YSZ Interlayer for AAO Based Thin Film Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: These phenomena caused by high density of oxygen vacancies in high Y2O3 concentrated PEALD YSZ interlayer, which helps oxygen incorporation reactions at cathode-interlayer interface.
Titulo: Effects of Nanoscale PEALD YSZ Interlayer for AAO Based Thin Film Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Therefore, cathodic polarization loss related with oxygen reduction reactions was decreased, and then, performance and exchange current density were improved.
Titulo: Effects of Nanoscale PEALD YSZ Interlayer for AAO Based Thin Film Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Results of this study imply that insertion of simple PEALD YSZ interlayer at cathode-electrolyte interface efficiently improves performance and electrochemical characteristics of TF-SOFCs.
Titulo: Effects of Nanoscale PEALD YSZ Interlayer for AAO Based Thin Film Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
